minations, which
often take years of painstaking work to establish. That includes sifting th=
rough the documentation that a professional army creates as it carries out =
its work=E2=80=94documentation that, according to the State Department=E2=
=80=99s report, Israel has not provided in full. While the I.D.F. has share=
